elements.name: Navigate user to 'Nationwide mortgage Page' as a New User

steps.name: User navigates to Mortgage rates for 'New mortgage customer'
'Search for a Nationwide mortgage' Page should be displayed

elements.name: Find a mortgage rate for New User

steps.name: when user is on the 'Search for a Nationwide mortgage' Page
the user selects No for Do you have a Nationwide mortgage option
I m changing lender' Option for 'What type of mortgage are you looking for?' menu
Clicks on Find a Mortgage Rate button
the user applies the first filter by 'Mortgage type = Fixed'
the user selects the second filter by 'Deal period = 2 yr Fixed, 3 yr Fixed, 5 yr Fixed, 10 yr Fixed'
And the user applies the third filter by 'Product fee = With Fee'
